<section id="overview">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="text-center fade-in">
      <h2 class="section-title">Workshop Overview</h2>
    </div>

    <p class="workshop-overview-text fade-in">
      This half-day workshop (date and venue to be announced) brings together the global mobile manipulation community to present
      results from the EBiM Competition, hear from leading researchers in real-world bimanual manipulation,
      and discuss the future of community-driven benchmarking. The workshop is the third phase of our
      coordinated benchmarking initiative — see the <a href="competition.html">Competition page</a> for
      benchmark details. Open to the global robotics community.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>


